text: Kamieńczyk may refer to the following places in Poland: *Kamieńczyk, Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Kamieńczyk, Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship (north-central Poland) *Kamieńczyk, Sokołów County in Masovian Voivodeship (east-central Poland) *Kamieńczyk, Wyszków County in Masovian Voivodeship (east-central Poland) *Kamieńczyk, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship (north Poland)
title: Kamieńczyk
